description: Funny because of the wordplay on tentacles.
title: Ticklish Octopus
n_1: Diver Dan approaches Olly, the friendly octopus, underwater.
c1_1: Hey Olly, ready for a laugh?
n_2: Dan reaches out and starts tickling Olly.
n_3: Olly squirms and giggles, tentacles flailing.
c1_3: How many tickles does it take?
n_4: Dan counts each tickle on Olly's tentacles.
